Flavortext: Echoing from ancient times, its ghostly form strikes terror, a spectral predator from a forgotten age.

Name: Shadowpounce Panther
Text: Ambush: An enemy Unit was deployed adjacently this Turn. Unearth: You may move this.
Flavortext: Master of the jungle's dark heart, its every step is a silent threat, a hunter cloaked in near-invisible menace.

Name: Shardtooth
Text: Ambush: A Unit was deployed this Turn. Unearth: An adjacent friendly Unit gains Ward.

Name: Spectra Stick Bug
Text: Ally of Insect: You may deploy an Insect from your Hand.
Flavortext: Among the greenery, it thrives as nature's artful imitator, a spectral insect hiding in plain sight.

Name: Sunflower Sprite
Text: Whenever a friendly Nature Unit is deployed adjacently, gain +2 Power.
Flavortext: As the sun's warmth bathes the world, it spreads its wings of harmony, a sprite that nurtures unity among nature's children.

Name: Sylvan Gamekeeper
Text: Ritual of Hunter: Up to three friendly Units with the lowest Powers gain +1 Power.
Flavortext: Ritual

Name: Tainted Jade Monstrosity
Text: Deploy: Crystallize the top two Cards of your Deck. Each Player buries three Crystals.
Flavortext: A creature of both life and decay, it embodies the Tainted Jade's perilous dance with nature's hidden forces.

Name: Tainted Jade Mycomancer
Text: Ally of Insect or Plant: You may bury this to deploy a friendly Insect or Plant Crystal adjacently.
Flavortext: From his vials emerge not just elixirs, but legions of insects, bred for battle's chaotic dance.

Name: Tiger Matriarch
Text: Deploy: Another friendly Nature Unit in this Lane gains +2 Power and Ward.
Flavortext: Sovereign of stripes and fangs, she embodies the jungle's heart, fierce and nurturing in her dominion.

Name: Trickster Sprite
Text: Deploy: You may return an adjacent friendly Unit to your Hand to gain +3 Power.
Flavortext: Bounce

Name: Venomleaf Croaker
Text: Deploy: Gains +1 Power for each adjacent Plant.
Flavortext: Leafy and lethal, a true monarch of the underbrush.

Name: Venus Flytrap
Text: Ambush: An enemy Unit was deployed adjacently this Turn. Unearth: Bury an adjacent enemy Unit with 4 or less Power.
Flavortext: What appears a mere plant masks a deadly trap, capable of snapping shut on much more than flies.

Name: Verdant Sakura Tree
Text: Crystallize: All friendly Plants gain +1 Power.
Flavortext: Atop the mountains, where life was thought to wither, it stands as a testament to nature's enduring beauty, a bloom eternal.

Name: Forgotten Ancient
Text: Ambush: This Turn, your Opponent conquered this Lane. Unearth: Unearth all adjacent Units.
Flavortext: Life leads to Death, and Death calls back Life.

Name: Locust Swarm
Text: Deploy: You may deploy an Insect from your Hand.
Flavortext: In their buzzing, a grim prophecy fulfilled; fields and hopes alike are consumed beneath their dark cloud.

Name: Necroconut Crab
Text: Deploy: Gain +1 Power for each buried Unit and buried Crystal.
Flavortext: Giant Demon Coconut Crab

Name: Rotting Alicorn
Text: Deploy: You may copy the Ability of another Unit.
Flavortext: Once pure, now tainted, it mirrors the darkest magics, twisting them with its own corruption.

Name: Tainted Jade Initiate
Flavortext: Embracing the jungle's forbidden elixirs, he communes with spirits unseen, a disciple of mysteries dark and profound.

Name: Abyssal Silencer
Text: Deploy: Bury an adjacent enemy Unit with equal or lower Power than this.
Flavortext: An assassin cloaked in the stillness of the abyss, where space bends to his will.

Name: Blightcoven Puppeteer
Text: Deploy: You may unearth an adjacent friendly Unit.
Flavortext: Every pull, every twitch, an orchestrated horror; the dance of the damned begins.

Name: Bloodthrone Ambassador
Text: Ritual: You may play an additional Unit this Turn.
Flavortext: Ritual

Name: Bloodthrone Familiar
Text: Crystallize: Unleash <?><?><?><?><?>: Unearth a friendly Undead Unit. When this gets buried, obscure 2.
Flavortext: Soaring through the night, it gathers whispers and secrets, loyal only to its vampiric sovereign.

Name: Bloodthrone Sovereign
Text: Ritual: Gain +4 Power. Ritual: Gain +4 Power.
Flavortext: Her throne, a monument to eternal night; her will, an unyielding dominion over darkness.

Name: Carnage Hornet
Text: Ambush: A Unit was deployed adjacently this Turn. Unearth: You may bury an adjacent friendly Unit to gain its Power.
Flavortext: In the buzz of its wings, one hears the whispers of merciless destruction.

Name: Champion from Hell
Text: Deploy: Your Opponent buries all of their adjacent Units except one.
Flavortext: How can your meager mortal minds not grasp the concept of 'one versus one'?

Name: Colorgorger
Text: Crystallize: If you control a Demon Unit, bury an enemy Crystal.
Flavortext: It nibbles away at colors, sapping strength from the very essence of its prey.

Name: Dark Spoon
Text: Deploy: Your Opponent puts a Card from their Hand beneath their Deck.
Flavortext: Beware the kitchenware that whispers secrets of chaos.

Name: Dawnbreak Wendigo
Text: Deploy: If you are trailing in Lanes, draw a card.
Flavortext: trail

Name: Depthdragger
Text: Deploy: Put any number of Cards from your Hand at the Bottom of your Deck and draw that many plus one.
Flavortext: Artifact

Name: Discarded Abomination
Text: Deploy: Gain Fear. Crystallize: Obscure 2 for each Lane you trail by.
Flavortext: Obscure

Name: Doomgaze Overlord
Text: Start of your Turn: Randomly obscure 1 or gain +2 Power.
Flavortext: Obscure

Name: Dread Cryptlord
Text: Deploy: If you are trailing in Lanes, all friendly Undead Unit gain +2 Power.
Flavortext: trail

Name: Emissary of Darkness
Text: Deploy: Draw the top Demon of your Deck. Shuffle your Deck.
Flavortext: Beneath a starless sky, the Emissary's incantations echo, as demons heed his silent call.

Name: Fatepeek Imp
Text: Deploy: Obscure once.
Flavortext: Obscure

Name: Forsaken Chronicler
Text: When this gets buried, draw a Card.
Flavortext: His quill dips in secrets as dark as blood, chronicling the silent reign of the Forsaken over the city's heart.

Name: Forsaken Serenader
Text: Deploy: Glimpse twice for each adjacent Void Unit.
Flavortext: In the dim light, his fingers dance across ivory, each note a whisper of timeless longing.

Name: Foul Corruptor
Text: Ritual: All friendly Void Units gain +1 Power.
Flavortext: In her gaze lies the downfall of purity; in her touch, the rot of empires.

Name: Ghoulflesh Devourer
Text: Whenever an enemy Unit with less Power is deployed adjacently, gain +1 Power.
Flavortext: Feasting on the meek, it grows ever stronger, a monstrous amalgam of death and dragon might.

Name: Gravebound Ghoul
Text: When this gets buried, an adjacent friendly Unit gains Power equal to this Unit's Power.
Flavortext: In the echo of a necromancer's neglect, it haunts, forever confined to its unintended crypt.

Name: Graverobber
Text: Deploy: You may return a friendly Construct Unit to your Hand.
Flavortext: In the dead of night, where tombstones loom, he finds kin amidst the gloom.

Name: Greedspawn
Text: Deploy: Gain +2 Power for each Rare Unit.
Flavortext: Every precious artifact, every rare jewel, amplifies its ravenous strength.

Name: Grim Titan
Text: Ally of Demon: Crystallize the top two Cards of your Deck and bury them.
Flavortext: Empty Crystal

Name: Grinning Amphora
Text: Deploy: Draw two Cards.
Flavortext: Its grin speaks of boundless greed, yet none truly know its purpose.

Name: Hellblade
Flavortext: Forged in the deepest fires, sheathed in eternal darkness.

Name: Hungry Shambler
Text: Deploy: Each Player buries one of their Crystals.
Flavortext: In its relentless shuffle, there's but one thought: feed, feed, feed.

Name: Ill-Tempered Imp
Flavortext: Within its volatile gaze lies a mischief only the brave dare to decipher.

Name: Intrusive Advisor
Text: Deploy: Draw two Cards, then put two Cards from your Hand to the bottom of the Deck.
Flavortext: A demon's counsel is a double-edged sword; one edge cuts through lies, the other through the listener.

Name: Meekbone Soldier
Text: Start of Turn: If you are trailing in Lanes, gain +1 Power.
Flavortext: trail

Name: Monarch of Shadows
Text: Start of Turn: Gain +1 Power for each buried Unit.
Flavortext: Each secret interred feeds his dark dominion; for him, every grave is a fount of power.

Name: Nethersilk Moth
Text: Whenever a friendly Void Unit is deployed adjacently, gain +2 Power.
Flavortext: Drawn to the void's cold embrace, each nearby shadow fuels its ghostly wings.

Name: Nightmare Penguin
Text: Deploy: Gain Fear.
Flavortext: What was whispered as a tale to scare children skulks in the darkness, a terrifying truth behind the fable.

Name: Nightreaper
Text: Deploy: Gain Fear. Bury a friendly Unit and a friendly Crystal.
Flavortext: Cloaked in midnight, he reaps souls with a blade that slices through fate and time, an eternal arbiter of the inevitable.

Name: Obsidian Scarab
Flavortext: Born from the darkest sands, its shell holds the secrets of eternity.

Name: Omenshadow
Text: Crystallize: Obscure 2.
Flavortext: Once ignored, her prophecies lingered in the air like mist—unseen, unheard, unwelcome. Now, she weaves the future with her own hands, a dark tapestry to force the eyes of the world wide open.

Name: Possessed Vermin Brood
Text: Ambush: An enemy Unit was deployed adjacently this Turn. Unearth: Gain Taunt.
Flavortext: A swarm tainted by darkness, their numbers are as endless as their hunger.

Name: Purple Crusader
Text: Whenever an enemy Unit of a different Realm is deployed adjacently, gain +1 Power.
Flavortext: With every swing of his blade, he sought to cleave the dark. But the void is patient; it seeped into his will, transforming his resolve into the very essence of what he once vanquished.

Name: Reborn Stargazer
Text: Start of your Turn: You may bury this to glimpse 3. Unearth: Obscure 3.
Flavortext: Once a herald of dawn, now a specter of dusk, it yearns for the light it has lost.

Name: Relentless Guardian
Text: When this gets buried, unearth it and bury a friendly Crystal.
Flavortext: "Warn...ing: Bl-blight, it creeps... I-I, still s-stand. Fight, must keep... Dark, d-deep. Not... give in."

Name: Runic Arachnid
Text: Ambush: An enemy Unit was deployed adjacently this Turn. Unearth: Copy the 'Deploy' ability of an adjacent enemy Unit and return that Unit to its Owners Hand.
Flavortext: Its webs drip with ancient curses, a trap not just for the flesh, but for the essence of magic itself.

Name: Sanguine Teapot
Text: Deploy: Your Opponent buries two Crystals.
Flavortext: "Item #0871: One (1) teapot, ceramic, seemingly benign but reputedly infused with malevolent energies. Note: Handle with care (and perhaps a prayer). Recommend storage: Restricted section, far from any actual tea ceremonies."

Name: Shadowsting Scorpion
Text: Ambush: An enemy Unit was deployed adjacently this Turn. Unearth: Bounce an adjacent Unit.
Flavortext: Death's whisper on eight silent legs.

Name: Shiverskull
Text: Deploy: All friendly Void Units gain Fear.
Flavortext: His every step is a reminder of mortality's cruel jest; his blade, a sharp retort.

Name: Shroom Behemoth
Flavortext: A colossal fusion of fungus and might, looming large from the forest's hidden depths.

Name: Shrouded Trickster
Text: Crystallize: Until end of turn, all buried Crystals become all Realms.
Flavortext: The demon, in its naïve malice, delights in the havoc of the blight, oblivious to the fact that it is but a pawn in a game played by shadows far deeper than its own dark whims.

Name: Skull Crow
Text: Deploy: Your Opponent buries one of their Units.
Flavortext: With eyes like ghostly lanterns, the guardian of the graveyards watches from above.

Name: Slumbering Fiend
Text: Unearth: Gain +6 Power.
Flavortext: They mourned him, as is the way of the living, until the grave unbound him. There he stood again among them, a presence both familiar and unsettling, marked by the passage through death's own door.

Name: Symbiotic Crawler
Text: Deploy: Another friendly Void Unit in this Lane gains +1 Power and Fear.
Flavortext: In the shadow of its tendrils, life withers, feeding this sinister, parasitic growth.

Name: The Forsaken King
Text: Ritual of Angel: Gain +2 Power, Taunt and Ward. Ritual of Demon: Draw 3 Cards.
Flavortext: In his fall, a kingdom was born, straddling the blurred lines between redemption and ruin.

Name: Thoughtfeaster
Text: Deploy: Gain Fear. Obscure once. Reveal the bottom Card of your Opponent's Deck and gain Power equal to its Power.
Flavortext: "Day 25: Another night, another visitation. Demon plays with us, a game of cat and mouse. It's there one moment, eyes gleaming and all, and then nothing but shadows. Men are on edge, their dreams poisoned by its taunting laughter."

Name: Tombstone Carver
Text: Deploy: Deploy the top Undead of your Deck buried adjacently. Shuffle your Deck.
Flavortext: In each chiseled line, a story ends.

Name: Umbral Nexus
Text: Deploy: Gain Taunt. Ascend: Void.
Flavortext: To the unsuspecting eye, it's merely flora, yet its roots delve deep, siphoning malice from the earth. Its pollen whispers dark thoughts to those who wander too close.

Name: Voidkiss Siren
Text: Ascend: Demon. Deploy: Your Opponent puts a Card from their Hand at the Bottom of their Deck. When this ascends, draw two Cards.
Flavortext: Her summoners are granted the boon of her power, but at the cost of witnessing her unfettered vengeance upon any slight, real or imagined, leaving them in silent horror at the chaos wrought in their name.

Name: Voidsinger
Text: Deploy: Choose one: - Your opponent shuffles 2 Cards from their Hand into their Deck. - Draw two Cards.
Flavortext: A serenade from the abyss, its melody fractures reality.

Name: Voodoo Doctor
Text: Whenever a Common Unit is deployed adjacently, obscure once.
Flavortext: By the light of a jade flame, the ritual unfolds, a macabre spectacle of devotion. The cultists seek not salvation, but the embrace of a power so ancient, its name has been swallowed by the mists of time.

Name: Whispering Tome
Text: Deploy: Search your Deck for a Card and draw it. Shuffle your Deck.
Flavortext: Decimus's folly was believing he could master the tome's ancient power without consequence. With every incantation learned, his essence was siphoned away, replaced by a darkness eager to spread beyond the confines of its pages.

Name: Choking Vines
Text: Deploy: Bury a friendly Crystal to glimpse 1.
Flavortext: The forests whisper of a creeping doom, one that leeches the vitality from the very soil, rendering the land barren of its arcane gifts.

Name: Clocktower Drake
Flavortext: Ticking gears and whirring cogs give life to this marvel; a testament to mortal genius soaring high in the sky.

Name: Crusader of the Wastelands
Text: Whenever an enemy Unit of a different Realm is deployed adjacently, gain +1 Power.
Flavortext: Amidst the desolation of the wasteland, every drop of water is bloodshed, and every shelter is a battleground, contested by the land's savage inheritors.

Name: Crystalbane Glutton
Text: Deploy: Bury three friendly Crystals to draw a Card.
Flavortext: The Crystalblight, an arcane affliction, devours the land's magic, turning sanctuaries into silent tombs and vibrant forests into graveyards of petrified wood.

Name: Crystalline Parasite
Text: Deploy: Bury two friendly Crystals to crystallize the top Card of your Deck.
Flavortext: Where once there was an abundance of arcane energy, now lies a thirsting emptiness, a testament to the ravages of a silent, unseen hunger.

Name: Fortune's Favorite
Text: Ascend.
Flavortext: He walks the earth lightly, for he belongs not to this world but to the ether, where ascension awaits the pure of heart.

Name: Mini Golem
Flavortext: Carved from the smallest rocks, yet its resolve stands as tall as the mountains.

Name: Null Ghost
Text: Deploy: Gain +2 Power for each friendly empty Crystal.
Flavortext: Empty Crystal

Name: Realmshifter
Text: This Card has all Realms.
Flavortext: To shift between worlds is to master the dance of existence.

Name: Shapeshifter
Text: This Card always has all Types.
Flavortext: One moment a whisper, the next a roar. Who will he be today?
